- "preliminary trials" corresponds to the condition of having an identification greater than 50;
- "shine brightly in the experimental cosmos" indicates the source being 'experiment';
- "zenith of splendor" refers to the maximum score of the protein structure;
- "catalogue in ascending order of their radiant glow" implies ordering the results by the maximum score in ascending order.
